name: preLoggingMultiDocs

testSteps.description: Given that I'm logged in to PreLogging page

children.description: When i open page from sidebar menu: {Accounts Payable,Pre-Registration,Pre-Logging}

testSteps.description: Then the 'Payment Information' form and its contents should show up
When I set the 'Supplier' to 'AG STAR CONSTRUCTION AND TRADING CO. LTD'
When I set the 'Invoice Number' to 'rcXDuMNN6S'
When I set the 'Currency' to 'USD'
When I click the 'Continue' button
When I select the first Bank Account and click 'Submit' button if modal exist
Then the 'Payment Amount' form and Its contents should show up
When I set the 'Gross Amount' to '1000'
When I set the 'Tax Area' to 'KF10'
When I click the 'Continue' button
Then the 'Preliminary Distribution Account' modal and its contents should show up
When I set the modal 'Description' to 'TEST 1'
When I click on 'Continue' button from modal
Then the 'Invoice Pre registration successfully created' modal should show up
When I click on 'Continue' button from modal
Then the 'Payment Information' form and its contents should show up
When I set the 'Supplier' to '25384'
When I set the 'Invoice Number' to '5TxnjhDgL2'
When I set the 'Currency' to 'USD'
When I click the 'Continue' button
When I select the first Bank Account and click 'Submit' button if modal exist
When I set the 'Gross Amount' to '2000'
When I set the 'Tax Area' to 'KF10'
When I click the 'Continue' button
Then the 'Preliminary Distribution Account' modal and its contents should show up
When I set the modal 'Description' to 'TEST 2'
When I click on 'Continue' button from modal
Then the 'Invoice Pre registration successfully created' modal should show up
When I click on 'Continue' button from modal
Then the 'Payment Information' form and its contents should show up
When I set the 'Supplier' to '118173'
When I set the 'Invoice Number' to 'T9uYmNIDJm'
When I set the 'Currency' to 'USD'
When I click the 'Continue' button
When I select the first Bank Account and click 'Submit' button if modal exist
When I set the 'Gross Amount' to '3000'
When I set the 'Tax Area' to 'KF10'
When I click the 'Continue' button
Then the 'Preliminary Distribution Account' modal and its contents should show up
When I set the modal 'Description' to 'TEST 3'
When I click on 'Continue' button from modal
Then the 'Invoice Pre registration successfully created' modal should show up
When I click on 'Exit' button from modal
When I open the 'Batch Posting' page
When I set the 'Batch Number' using the previously generated value from Pre registration modal
When i clear the batch type field
When i click on search button
Then the batch posting search results should show up
Then the post button of the first batch posting search result should be disabled
When I click 'See More' button
Then the post button of the first batch posting search result should be enabled
When i click post button
Then the 'Batch Successfully Posted' notification message should show up
